{"tid":1218833,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"差佬打記者喺香港可能無乜人理 但喺外國係好大鑊","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:05:20.000Z","uid":42379,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"af6b6a18a148e973cb89aa36c28dee083785093b","tid":1218833,"uid":42379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:54:42.000Z","msg":"港台啱啱喺Facebook post咗段片係班狗喺金鐘道「記你老母」同清晰睇到佢哋揮棍毆打同追趕記者。<br />\n<br />\n喺香港嘅你可能會覺得 屌黑警係咁架啦，<br />\n但喺國際社會，好多人都唔會expect警察會咁做，<br />\n同時佢哋都唔知香港黑警嘅惡行。所以我將呢條加咗英文字幕，希望大家會幫手share出去，無論係twitter、reddit或者Facebook都好，<br />\n等多啲外國人都睇到呢一班黑警點嘗試打壓新聞自由。唔該曬大家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eLpjnsC7WAs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeLpjnsC7WAs&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=fedfcc40\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eLpjnsC7WAs</a>"},{"pid":"4a9b3a056c63db751ba6c3261c0ac9d6b7629493","tid":1218833,"uid":74278,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"香港係好多人理<br />\n冇差佬理姐"},{"pid":"7e10aa2cc6127122c40e539e004fa513df1144f2","tid":1218833,"uid":174121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2cdc80cf3df4bdafe706929110e9d48cadbd4761","tid":1218833,"uid":42379,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"4a9b3a056c63db751ba6c3261c0ac9d6b7629493","tid":1218833,"uid":74278,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"香港係好多人理<br />\n冇差佬理姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"唔夠，要多啲外國人知<br />\n有個朋友被個外國朋友問點睇香港發生緊嘅&rdquo;riots&rdquo;<br />\n證明唔係好多外國人知現實係發生緊咩事！<br />\n我哋要畀世界知，邊個先係暴徒"},{"pid":"f93499434252466d4093c0655f596b20e4dbd27f","tid":1218833,"uid":74278,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2cdc80cf3df4bdafe706929110e9d48cadbd4761","tid":1218833,"uid":42379,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"4a9b3a056c63db751ba6c3261c0ac9d6b7629493","tid":1218833,"